Yakut looked around seeing Raven and Lynn could hold down the fort while Yakut could show Christanna a tour of TRV.<br>
<br>
&quot;So? Tanna, would you like a tour of my snowy cold lands?&quot;<br>
<br>
Yakut smiled. She loved her happy little home. Not only was her lands right next door to Scynthia, home of Alysia and Belle Yakut's good friends, it was the place she had a connection too. <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§

