<br>
She glanced around the village and saw Lynn there. Raven hadn't seen Lynn for so long. Though the two never really had time to spend together before, they were sisters nonetheless. But in this time of darkness . . . Raven was an only child.<br>
<br>
She walked through the crowd of amazons and up towards her Mother standing before the two women.<br>
<br>
&quot;Mother . . . I have been meaning to speak with you on something. A letter arrived earlier from Scynthia. Alysia has returned to Scynthia. The Amazon Nation no longer shall mourn for her passing.&quot;<br>
<br>
It was true, Alysia was back. But not even Raven knew of the severity of what had happened with Alysia and Belle.<br>
<br>
She then turned her eyes to the other woman.<br>
<br>
&quot;Goddess of Peace hmm? With no offense to you, but in my eyes the only power that brings peace is that of our Ancients.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(1/18/02 8:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> (Its ok)</span><hr size=1> Yakut was relieved to find out of Alysia's well-being. She was sort of curious as to how she came back but no matter. She smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ahh, So the Ruler of Scynthia lives. Yet another reason to rejoice in the name of the Ancients.&quot;<br>
<br>
Yakut looked to Raven as she spoke to Tanna.<br>
<br>
&quot;Raven, she knows she holds no power here. She has entered our tribe, I am training her in our ways and the art of shamanism.&quot;<br>
<br>
It was odd calling shamanism an art, to Yakut it was life. Yakut totally did not want to upset Raven with having a goddess around but Christanna was very different from any other god. Yakut hoped Raven would recognized the immortality in her own blood and have some tolerance for Christanna. <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§

