Yakut smiled as she took off her shaman headress and laid it on the table next to her bed. She ran her fingers through her hair.<br>
<br>
[OOC- Yakut has never been seen with her headress off in any of her pics so I dont know what color hair she really has but I as her mun chose blonde.]<br>
<br>
&quot;Christanna, I must say your amazingly beautiful.&quot;<br>
<br>
The day Yakut thought would never arrive has. She was in love. <br>
